PrecisAmendments to the CUSTOMS BONDED WAREHOUSES REGULATIONS which establish certain procedural rights when a licence is suspended, abolish restrictions on the number of times that ownership of bonded goods may be transferred, allow for greater flexibility in determining minimum security deposits, and eliminate discrepancies between the English and French versions or make technical clarifications.
